message.body: Hey! Don't know if you're back. Wondering if u cld give a ride to airport thurs night at 7:30. I won't need car until Monday. No pressure, just wondering.
Hey!!! I'm back, reluctantly. Thursday I have a meeting after class 5-6:30 then meeting friends at 30th street station. They are supposed to arrive from NYC at 7:30 :(
Vt for Labor Day. Let's get together soon!
